---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ask a Question" description="Submit a question about therapy, emotions, or personal growth. Katie might answer it in a future post.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-24 px-8 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="blob-sage w-72 h-72 -top-36 -left-36 absolute"></div>
    <div class="blob-sage w-56 h-56 top-20 -right-28 absolute"></div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto relative">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="accent-line mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-6">Ask a Question</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal-light max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Submit a question and I might answer it in a future post.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Form -->
      <form class="bg-white rounded-xl p-12 border border-cream-dark shadow-sm mb-12">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <label for="question" class="block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal mb-4">
            Your Question
          </label>
          <textarea
            id="question"
            name="question"
            rows="6"
            placeholder="What's on your mind? Ask about therapy, emotions, relationships, personal growth..."
            class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-md border border-cream-dark bg-cream/30 focus:border-sage focus:outline-none focus:bg-white transition-colors resize-none"
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <label for="context" class="block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal mb-4">
            Any Context (Optional)
          </label>
          <textarea
            id="context"
            name="context"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Background that might help me understand where you're coming from..."
            class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-md border border-cream-dark bg-cream/30 focus:border-sage focus:outline-none focus:bg-white transition-colors resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              name="anonymous"
              class="w-5 h-5 rounded border-cream-dark text-sage focus:ring-sage"
              checked
            />
            <span class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">Keep my submission anonymous</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal mb-4">
            Email (Optional)
          </label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Only if you'd like to be notified when I respond"
            class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-md border border-cream-dark bg-cream/30 focus:border-sage focus:outline-none focus:bg-white transition-colors"
          />
          <p class="text-xs text-warm-gray mt-2">I won't share your email or use it for anything else.</p>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full bg-sage text-cream py-6 rounded-md hover:bg-sage-dark transition-colors font-medium"
        >
          Submit Question
        </button>
      </form>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sage/5 via-sage/10 to-sage/5 p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-sage">
        <h2 class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-4">A few things to know:</h2>
        <ul class="text-sm text-charcoal-light space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>I read every question but can't respond to all of them individually.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Selected questions may be answered in future essays or posts (anonymously, unless you specify otherwise).</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
            <span>This is not a substitute for therapy. I cannot provide personalized mental health advice through this form.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>If you're in crisis, please reach out to the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline or go to your nearest emergency room.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
